# STYLE:    DEFAULT
# AUTHOR:   NeverSink
# BUILDNOTES: Filter generated with NeverSink's FilterpolishZ and the domainlanguage Exo.
#
#------------------------------------
# LINKS TO LATEST VERSION AND FILTER EDITOR
